
1) Regression Testing:

   All in one go:

   EnvName.bat

   or:

   %vectorcast_dir%\clicast -lc tools execute commands.tmp false

   or:

   %vectorcast_dir%\clicast -lc environment build EnvName.env
   %vectorcast_dir%\clicast -e EnvName tools script run EnvName.tst
   %vectorcast_dir%\clicast -e EnvName execute batch
   %vectorcast_dir%\clicast -e EnvName reports custom management EnvName_management_report.html


2) Manage:

   REM Line 3: Fully build or rebuild environments and then execute all tests
   %VECTORCAST_DIR%\manage --project=Test_Campaign --build-execute --workspace=S:\Test_Campaign\build
 
   REM Line 4: Store the status in project database
   %VECTORCAST_DIR%\manage -¡Vproject=Test_Campaign --store-status
 
   REM Line 5: Generate HTML reports with full status of each environment in project
   %VECTORCAST_DIR%\manage --project=Test_Campaign --full-status=%FULL_REPORT_NAME% --output=%SharedLocationForReports%
